    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《The Art of Reflection》是一款第一人称谜题游戏、它探讨了穿越镜子的可能性。当你穿越镜子进入镜像世界时、会发生什么？在另一边、物体甚至是重力都不一样该怎么办？随着你掌握导航这个世界的技巧、展开复杂的反射路径。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290770/extras/a256928eae448a1425f2bf68b48ad046.poster.avif?t=1764608311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290770/extras/a256928eae448a1425f2bf68b48ad046.webm?t=1764608311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290770/extras/a256928eae448a1425f2bf68b48ad046.mp4?t=1764608311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的主要工具是一个快速缩放、它可以让你穿越镜子、瞬间跨越长距离、在空中轻松地以慢动作重新定位、等等。解决一个房间内的谜题、然后颠倒穿越同一结构的背面。一座迷宫般的建筑正等待你去揭开它隐藏的角落。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290770/extras/0a496de3fdfe54530f3838184f2622d9.poster.avif?t=1764608311\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290770/extras/0a496de3fdfe54530f3838184f2622d9.webm?t=1764608311\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290770/extras/0a496de3fdfe54530f3838184f2622d9.mp4?t=1764608311\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
